    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorb's family has a <strong>special destiny</strong>. When his mom catches him recording an embarrassing <strong>dance tutorial</strong>, she knows that he is ready. She hands him a <strong>magic ribbon</strong> that can open <strong>portals</strong> and sends him to space. He must now travel through the galaxy and defeat his opponents... in epic <strong>DANCE BATTLES</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Portal to the Cosmobeat is a <strong>narrative-driven Dance Game</strong> featuring <strong>unconventional movement controls</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the keys on your keyboard to select a limb of your choice and now... move your mouse to dance. Sounds easy to you? Prove it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/3b7177d085e85dd074952c13fba3295d.avif?t=1761820050\" width=620 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/2a352287431433a1db67c41a50fa7243.poster.avif?t=1761820050\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/2a352287431433a1db67c41a50fa7243.webm?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/2a352287431433a1db67c41a50fa7243.mp4?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open portals with your magic ribbon and travel through the galaxy.<br>You will <strong>challenge</strong> the best <strong>dancers</strong> in the universe while listening to the <strong>freshest beats</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At launch the game will feature a range of unique <strong>levels</strong>, each based on its own <strong>music genre</strong>, from <strong>Techno</strong> to <strong>Classical</strong> to <strong>J-Pop</strong>! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/75ffc49c131f043932235a64aea69184.avif?t=1761820050\" width=620 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/61bce08c7cae0469fc575148515b8c4e.poster.avif?t=1761820050\" width=620 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/61bce08c7cae0469fc575148515b8c4e.webm?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/61bce08c7cae0469fc575148515b8c4e.mp4?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow Gorb on his <strong>quest</strong> through the galaxy with hilarious <strong>dialogue</strong> and engaging <strong>cutscenes</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expect the unexpected on Gorb's <strong>interdimensional</strong> journey and challenge <strong>famous dancers</strong> from all over the <strong>Cosmobeat</strong>!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/361d0448ba8dfddeca463a62c3c85d31.avif?t=1761820050\" width=620 height=70 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/be6b9f31e1dc7213ad2ec57ac03a47af.poster.avif?t=1761820050\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/be6b9f31e1dc7213ad2ec57ac03a47af.webm?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064980/extras/be6b9f31e1dc7213ad2ec57ac03a47af.mp4?t=1761820050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use our game's <strong>unique mechanic</strong> and dance Gorb to the top!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy Gorb's <strong>clumsy</strong> dance <strong>moves</strong> in a variety of <strong>choreography</strong> and <strong>freestyle</strong> sections with a <strong>special twist</strong> for every <strong>dimension</strong> that is gonna keep you on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reach a new <strong>highscore</strong> and achieve <strong>GORBLIKE</strong> ratings!</p></li></ul>",
